  51.6.24 ESMF_VMLogSystem - LogSystem

   INTERFACE:
   subroutine ESMF_VMLogSystem(prefix, logMsgFlag, rc)

   ARGUMENTS:
     character(len=*),       intent(in),   optional  :: prefix
     type(ESMF_LogMsg_Flag), intent(in),   optional  :: logMsgFlag
     integer, intent(out),                 optional  :: rc

   DESCRIPTION:

   Log the VM.

   The arguments are:

   [prefix]
          String to prefix the log message. Default is no prefix.

   [logMsgFlag]
          Type of log message generated. See section [621]49.2.3 for a
          list of valid message types. Default is ESMF_LOGMSG_INFO.

   [rc]
          Return code; equals ESMF_SUCCESS if there are no errors.

